Prince Mangosuthu Buthelezi, says King Misuzulu kaZwelithini, is already on the throne. #eNCA​ Courtesy #DStv403 KWANONGOMA - Prince Mangosuthu Buthelezi, says King Misuzulu kaZwelithini, is already on the throne. This after clashes tempers flared at the royal palace when the Prince was named as the heir to the throne in his late mother, Queen Mantfombi's Dlamini Zulu. READ: WATCH: Amazulu Prime Minister, Mangosuthu Buthelezi addresses nation The Regent had stepped into the role after the passing of King Zwelithini in March. Watch the video above for more details on this story